      2. Spring jockey pulley.<br />
      3. Lower guide wheel.<br />
      4. Tape tension brake.<br />
      5. Reservoir No.1 entry door.<br />
      6. No.2 tape drive wheel.<br />
      7. Tape drive belt.<br />
      8. Tape Reservoir No.2.<br />
      9. Tape tension brake adjustment.<br />
      10. Quick release toggle.<br />
      11. Tape travel indicator.<br />
      12. Pilot light.<br />
      13. Red, green and white signalling lights.</div>
